{
  "stem": "2353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I won, and it was great, and I felt wonderful about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the way back-- this was outside of the town, outside of London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the way back to the station to go back to London, we were in a taxi, and we saw a newspaper, newspapers being hawked in the street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it had big headlines, something about the Nazis, and we made him stop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was the day when, what they called the-- when Hitler killed off about 2,000 of his own friends and men because they were rebelling against him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we thought well, maybe that's the end of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, we felt very good about this as long as there's all this revolution going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were very wrong about that because he only showed that if you did not agree with him-- I'm talking of Hitler-- you weren't going to live a very long time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we got to the hotel, and my father got very-- in a very bad mood all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we got to the hotel, he, he told me that the Germans had approached him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I had to come back to Germany to be on the German Olympic team.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, why should I go back?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father said, look, I don't force you into anything, but we were threatened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The family-- still living in Germany, of course-- we were threatened that if you don't come back, you have to-- you know, the consequences.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They can't guarantee what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, of course, I went back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, what else could I do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was such a peculiar situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
